  "text": "Primary cultures of rat hippocampal neurons were prepared from the hippocampi of 18-day-old fetuses as previously described [CITATION_1] . Neurons were transfected using the calcium phosphate precipitation method. Silencing of SNAP-25 was achieved via transfection of a pSUPER construct provided by T. Galli (Paris, France) [CITATION_2] . The cDNA for SNAP-25 and SNAP-25 were generously provided O. Rossetto (Padua, Italy).",
